// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3687 — Mass File Rename (ElDorado)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 2bee7698-df49-5144-85cf-3305c924b7d9

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
